## Overview

### The challenge

Users should be able to:

- View the optimal layout depending on their device's screen size
- See hover states for interactive elements


### Links

- Solution URL: [https://www.frontendmentor.io/solutions/3-column-preview-card-using-html5-and-css3-vOfjqAKwv](https://www.frontendmentor.io/solutions/3-column-preview-card-using-html5-and-css3-vOfjqAKwv)
